text: Planegg is a municipality in Munich, in Bavaria, Germany. It is on the river Würm, 13 km west of Munich (centre). == Twin towns == * Meylan, France, since 1987. * Bärenstein in Erzgebirge, since 1992. * Klausen in Südtirol, since 2006. * Didcot, United Kingdom, since 2012.Planegg und Didcot werden Partner, Münchner Merkur vom 30. März 2012 ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Munich (district)
